attributionInfo.brokerName: Beach Realty Of Little River Llc

data.description: East of 17 in Little River - Waterway Cove is where you will find this home.  Three Bedrooms, two baths, large two car garage, open floor plan, high ceilings in the living area, dining room area, large breakfast bar, white cabinets, split bedroom floor plan, laundry room, fenced in back yard, retractable awnings on the back patio and windows, private hallway to guest bedrooms, quaint neighborhood with small HOA fee, This needs a little work - but was loved by the current owners before moving to an assistant living facility.  Great Location close to beaches, waterfront in Little River, restaurants shopping, entertainment, doctors and hospitals.   NMB has the widest beach in town - and it is only minutes away! North Carolina Beaches are just a few extra minutes to the north of us.  The Carolinas have many things to offer - ESPECIALLY our beautiful weather all year around.  This home just needs a little TLC and it will be good as new!  New Roof and Water heater this year!  Don't let this great home pass you by!
